<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Send Enquiry | Estate Pro</title>

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">

<style>
  :root {
    --accent: #0ea5e9; /* Sky Blue */
    --accent-soft: #e0f2fe;
    --text-main: #0f172a;
    --text-light: #64748b;
    --bg-page: #f8fafc;
  }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    background-color: var(--bg-page);
    /* Subtle geometric pattern background */
    background-image: radial-gradient(#cbd5e1 0.5px, transparent 0.5px);
    background-size: 24px 24px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .enquiry-container {
    display: flex;
    max-width: 850px;
    width: 100%;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  /* Left Side - Info Panel */
  .info-panel {
    flex: 1;
    background: var(--accent);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #2563eb 100%);
    padding: 40px;
    color: white;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .info-panel h2 {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .info-panel p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .contact-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .contact-item i {
    width: 35px;
    height: 35px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  /* Right Side - Form */
  .form-panel {
    flex: 1.2;
    padding: 45px;
  }

  .form-panel h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: var(--text-main);
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }

  .form-group {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-main);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  input, textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px 15px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    background: #fcfcfc;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  input:focus, textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: white;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--accent-soft);
  }

  textarea {
    height: 100px;
    resize: none;
  }

  button {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--text-main);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 14px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  button:hover {
    background: #334155;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* Mobile Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .enquiry-container {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .info-panel {
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .form-panel {
      padding: 30px;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="enquiry-container">
  <div class="info-panel">
    <h2>Let's Talk About Your Dream Home</h2>
    <p>Have questions about this property? Send us a message and our expert agent will guide you through the process.</p>
    
    <div class="contact-item">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i>
      <span>Response within 2-4 hours</span>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-item">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i>
      <span>Verified Property Agent</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="form-panel">
    <h3>Send an Enquiry</h3>
    
    <form method="POST" action="/enquiry">
      <input type="hidden" name="property_id" value="<%= propertyId %>">
      <input type="hidden" name="agent_id" value="<%= agentId %>">

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Full Name</label>
        <input type="text" name="buyer_name" placeholder="Enter your name" required>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>Phone Number</label>
        <input type="tel" name="buyer_phone" placeholder="+91 00000 00000" required>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label>How can we help?</label>
        <textarea name="message" placeholder="Ask about price, location, or schedule a visit..."></textarea>
      </div>

      <button type="submit">Send Enquiry</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>